<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida96a69b2-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s2348"><num value="2348">§ 2348.</num><heading> Inventories of supplies not to be increased</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Inventories of supplies for elements of the armed forces may not be increased for the purpose of transferring supplies under the authority of this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida96a69b3-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/96/323/s2/a">Pub. L. 96–323, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1980-08-04">Aug. 4, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/1018">94 Stat. 1018</ref>, § 2328; amended <ref href="/us/pl/97/22/s11/a/8">Pub. L. 97–22, § 11(a)(8)</ref>, <date date="1981-07-10">July 10, 1981</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/95/138">95 Stat. 138</ref>; renumbered § 2348, <ref href="/us/pl/99/145/tXIII/s1304/a/1">Pub. L. 99–145, title XIII, § 1304(a)(1)</ref>, <date date="1985-11-08">Nov. 8, 1985</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/99/741">99 Stat. 741</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/99/661/dA/tXI/s1104/e">Pub. L. 99–661, div. A, title XI, § 1104(e)</ref>, <date date="1986-11-14">Nov. 14, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3965">100 Stat. 3965</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/189/dA/tIX/s931/e/1">Pub. L. 101–189, div. A, title IX, § 931(e)(1)</ref>, <date date="1989-11-29">Nov. 29, 1989</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/103/1535">103 Stat. 1535</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
